{
  "stem": "21437.7",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then there were moments where you felt, you know, that you-- you can fool yourself just that much.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But, to me, it seemed that this is occasionally, that this is-- it seemed occasionally, that if somebody said something like this it was hard for me to believe.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So sometimes I responded in a certain way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, I think that they want any witnesses if I know their mentality?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, so I was listening to this, and that wasn't very good, but I was listening to this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when suddenly there was nothing, I just couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was all off 17.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, I mean, a few hours later, we just sat there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just sat together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We huddled.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we-- we-- we sat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't-- we didn't want to move.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some of them were maybe running out, but I remember the sitting, you know, and the waiting, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We thought it's something-- before something happens, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the Russians hadn't arrived at this point?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were sitting, no, because they ran before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the morning, early in the morning, there was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a little while later, when we realized that nobody was there, we had bought-- we had the young inmates coming from Regensburg, from other boys coming inside.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And guess what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Within 48 hours, a lot of them, who were older than I was, they just paired off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Paired off.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And till today, they got married later on, sometimes they don't-- somebody says that they-- they got married first, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just paired off and they became a couple.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, they went away.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
